# Data attribution

The word lists bundled in this repository for tests and benchmarks are derived
from open linguistic datasets:

- `benches/data/en.tsv.zst` — English expressions with frequency percentiles
- `benches/data/sv.tsv.zst` — Swedish expressions with frequency percentiles
- `src/search/tests/sv_a.tsv` — small Swedish sample (words starting with "a")

Each row is `path<TAB>percentile<TAB>expression_index` — factual word/frequency
data with no original prose.

## Sources

- **PanLex** (https://panlex.org) — the PanLex database is released into the
  public domain under the Creative Commons CC0 1.0 Universal dedication.
- **Wiktionary** (https://www.wiktionary.org) — Wiktionary content is licensed
  under CC BY-SA and the GFDL.

These files are included only as representative input for running the test
suite and benchmarks. They are not part of the `wordtree` library code, which
is licensed separately (see `LICENSE-MIT` / `LICENSE-APACHE`).

If you redistribute these data files, retain this attribution. When in doubt
about reuse, consult the upstream license terms linked above.
